|<span data-ttu-id="10de7-9826">0x8020832B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="10de7-9826">0x8020832B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="10de7-9827">-2145352917</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="10de7-9827">-2145352917</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="10de7-9828">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_JOINLENGTHMISMATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="10de7-9828">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_JOINLENGTHMISMATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="10de7-9829">O comprimento da coluna de entrada '%1' não é igual ao comprimento da coluna de referência '%2' à qual está sendo feita a correspondência.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="10de7-9829">The length of input column '%1' is not equal to the length of the reference column '%2' that it is being matched against.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="10de7-9835">0x8020832E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="10de7-9835">0x8020832E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="10de7-9836">-2145352914</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="10de7-9836">-2145352914</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="10de7-9837">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_TOOMANYEXACTMATCHCOLUMNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="10de7-9837">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_TOOMANYEXACTMATCHCOLUMNS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="10de7-9838">Há mais de 16 junções de correspondência exata, assim o desempenho pode não ser o ideal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="10de7-9838">There are more than 16 exact match joins, so performance may not be optimal.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="10de7-9839">Reduza o número de junções de correspondência exata para melhorar o desempenho.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="10de7-9839">Reduce the number of exact match joins to improve performance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="10de7-9840">O SQL Server tem como limite 16 colunas por índice, será usado o índice invertido para todas as pesquisas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="10de7-9840">SQL Server has a limit of 16 columns per index, the inverted index will be used for all lookups.</span></span>|
